<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Shrine_of_Remembrance&action=edit&section=1.php.html" title="Edit section: History">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="History">History</span></h2>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:252px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Melbourne_CBD_(View_from_the_top_of_Shrine_of_Remembrance).jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/63/Melbourne_CBD_(View_from_the_top_of_Shrine_of_Remembrance).jpg/250px-Melbourne_CBD_(View_from_the_top_of_Shrine_of_Remembrance).jpg" width="250" height="166" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/63/Melbourne_CBD_%28View_from_the_top_of_Shrine_of_Remembrance%29.jpg/375px-Melbourne_CBD_%28View_from_the_top_of_Shrine_of_Remembrance%29.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/63/Melbourne_CBD_%28View_from_the_top_of_Shrine_of_Remembrance%29.jpg/500px-Melbourne_CBD_%28View_from_the_top_of_Shrine_of_Remembrance%29.jpg 2x" /></a>
