<li id="cite_note-BuildingWithASoul-25"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-BuildingWithASoul_25-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation book"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://web.archive.org/web/20080719175035/http:/shrine.org.au/retrievemedia.asp?Media_ID=416">"Victoria's National Memorial"</a>. <i>History of the shrine ... a building with a soul</i>. Shrine of Remembrance. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.shrine.org.au/retrievemedia.asp?Media_ID=416">the original</a> on 19 July 2008<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://web.archive.org/web/20080719175035/http:/shrine.org.au/retrievemedia.asp?Media_ID=416">http://web.archive.org/web/20080719175035/http://shrine.org.au/retrievemedia.asp?Media_ID=416</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 12 July 2008</span>.</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Hill-26"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Hill_26-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Hill (2003)</span></li>
